                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">McCormick</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-03-02">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 2, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay informs Mr. McCormick that according to press reports the mining
                    districts in Korea near the frontier have been occupied by Russian troops, and
                    although it is believed that all possible consideration and security will be
                    given to neutral Americans and their interests, an assurance in this respect
                    would be acceptable to the United States Government.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
